## PLUGIN CATEGORIES

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

**🎬 VIDEO EFFECTS**
• Glitch, VHS, Retro
• Light Leaks, Lens Flares
• Film Grain, Noise
• Blur, Sharpen, Soft Focus
• Chromatic Aberration
• Chroma Key (Green Screen)
• Slow Mo/Twixtor

**🔄 TRANSITIONS**
• Smooth Transitions
• Glitch Transitions
• Zoom, Pan, Spin
• Light, Flash, Blur
• Slide, Wipe, Push
• 3D Transitions
• Motion Graphics transitions

**🎨 LUTs (COLOR)**
• Cinematic (Hollywood look)
• Teal & Orange (blockbuster)
• Vintage, Retro, Film
• Instagram/TikTok filters
• Horror, Thriller mood
• Wedding, Romantic
• Corporate, Clean

**📝 TITLES & TEXT**
• Kinetic Typography
• 3D Titles
• Lower Thirds
• Callouts
• Credits (end cards)
• Intro/Outro templates

